{"tid":2037092,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（突發）5.27《和你唱國歌》","createTime":"2020-05-26T23:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T02:48:14.000Z","uid":76002,"like":227,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"8497f91817d0bbdb6c36e47119fb76fedb644d88","tid":2037092,"uid":76002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:12:49.000Z","msg":"呼籲各位岩岩瞓醒唔知今日有咩做ge<span style=\"color: green;\">和理非</span>手足參加今日中午「和你唱國歌」！<br />\n<br />\n5月27日 Lunchtime 全香港各區各大最近自己ge商場中庭<br />\n等我哋話俾全世界國際社會知，香港人ge國歌係咩！<br />\n我哋唔會屆服係中共之下！<br />\n<br />\n「唔要中共惡歌，只要香港榮光！」<br />\n「Two countries! Two systems! Two <span style=\"color: gold;\">anthems</span>!」"},{"pid":"c2d50d8de993ab4a0b0f4078c0e5f01470dd63be","tid":2037092,"uid":76002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:13:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"530f8c72be45314fc037620404ff0c8782821c74","tid":2037092,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:13:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98a8d8c4265acc1f1d284415b5cfea7b582db4c","tid":2037092,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4bdbb9dcba88d76311a408bf41ffbd6243132f","tid":2037092,"uid":4239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9031a480e29f019da7bb954be2deab2ee5969705","tid":2037092,"uid":266011,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:14:47.000Z","msg":"can ah ok i like shopping"},{"pid":"9f43ee8606dccc25b4aff318ae389e36c7e9bd58","tid":2037092,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:15:05.000Z","msg":"加手勢"},{"pid":"0e14ed745a737117299bee42d21d15cf8f16ba82","tid":2037092,"uid":124859,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:16:02.000Z","msg":"hunger game 舉高3指"},{"pid":"b9bda8072b490fb4612b429b58ac078f3ab31fd5","tid":2037092,"uid":241171,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:17:12.000Z","msg":"改中午會重衰 而家繁忙時段 多人 中午少左人更加難搞<br />\n<br />\n同登陸一樣"},{"pid":"8c5f0123eafcf22e5591819b477fad619fb14edd","tid":2037092,"uid":76002,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:18:03.000Z","msg":"有關發起呢個行動ge緣由<br />\n<br />\n問1: 瞓之前唔係話開花三罷黎明行動架咩？<br />\n<br />\n答1: 因為尋晚支那01出咗報道話有足夠奶共狗議員通宵留守咗係立法會，加上熱狗鄭松泰自己fb佐證，所以堵路戰術已經馬上失效，加上預告埋有3500狗隻已經守緊立法會，所以基本上仲諗住令立法會<span style=\"color: red;\">重現612已經唔太可能</span><br />\n<br />\n問2: 咁我哋唔通由得班pk二讀？<br />\n<br />\n答2: 根據立法會主席大口狗自己講，會預留30小時傾條惡法，所以今日實際上未必二讀。Now出ge新聞係話6月4號先表決。所以<span style=\"color: red;\">議會入面可以交比泛民/熱狗頂住先</span>。<br />\n<br />\n問3: 我唔信01，唔信熱狗，唔信泛民！我哋要靠大家一齊開花塞鐵set rb拆政府設施先可以向政府施壓，增加管治成本，忙死班狗！你理得我，兄弟爬山嘛！<br />\n<br />\n答3: Ok ge，各有各做，不過開花ge話個focus就唔同曬，我覺得會<span style=\"color: red;\">變咗單純為開花而開花</span>。我難以預見中共會因為我哋做呢D野而唔推/暫緩/撤回国歌法。反而咁做就送子彈俾中共，即刻spin我哋做恐怖分子bilibala，而我哋開花係已經得唔到D咩正面效果，負面效果有手足比狗打比狗告、國際線又難打咗...etc 多到唔想數。BTW，花已開ge話，手足記得be water，搞清楚自己想做到D咩<br />\n<br />\n問4: 咁即係我哋咩都唔洗做？？<br />\n<br />\n答4: 唔係！我哋最逼切要做ge係<span style=\"color: red;\">針對国歌惡法ge民意表態</span>！要<span style=\"color: gold;\">話比全世界知</span>，我哋唔承認中共国歌係香港ge國歌！香港人必然拒絕国歌惡法，而屬於<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人ge國歌</span>，只有一首，就係《<span style=\"color: gold;\">願榮光歸香港</span>》"},{"pid":"38fca2815bb6cfb906f51e33bfc94c7b4377bd08","tid":2037092,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:18:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8ef9c79e37281dfe0cd0537dbed063d332225258","tid":2037092,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T23:20:27.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"9c0dc1042bdca7db4b6061278c8a557b0d2370df","tid":2037092,"uid":76002,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9bda8072b490fb4612b429b58ac078f3ab31fd5","tid":2037092,"uid":241171,"like"